<subSubSection id="C36696BB8E5FFFB2FF1AFD9ADAAEFD57" pageId="4" pageNumber="145" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BC3C5308E5FFFB2FF1AFD9ADAAEFD57" blockId="4.[163,1071,502,689]" pageId="4" pageNumber="145">
Comment: The distribution of 
<taxonomicName id="4C7CBEB38E5FFFB2FDA5FD9ADBA6FD90" baseAuthorityName="MOTSCHULSKY" baseAuthorityYear="1858" box="[540,731,609,630]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Astenus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="145" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="nigromaculatus">
<emphasis id="B90819228E5FFFB2FDA5FD9ADBA6FD90" box="[540,731,609,630]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="145">A. nigromaculatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
ranges from the Canary Islands and the Iberian Peninsula across North Africa to the Middle East (
<bibRefCitation id="EFEDB8C18E5FFFB2FCE8FD85DA89FD72" author="SMETANA A" box="[849,1012,638,660]" pageId="4" pageNumber="145" pagination="505 - 698" refId="ref7869" refString="SMETANA A. (2004): Staphylinidae, subfamilies Omaliinae - Dasycerinae, Phloeocharinae - Apaticinae, Piestinae - Staphylininae, pp. 237 - 272, 329 - 495, 505 - 698. - In: LOBL I. &amp; A. SMETANA (eds), Catalogue of Palaearctic Coleoptera. II. Hydrophiloidea - Histeroidea - Staphylinoidea. - Stenstrup, Apollo Books: 942 pp." type="book chapter" year="2004">SMETANA 2004</bibRefCitation>
). The species had already been recorded from 
<collectingCountry id="F36B85A08E5FFFB2FD82FD60DBBDFD57" box="[571,704,667,689]" name="Saudi Arabia" pageId="4" pageNumber="145">Saudi Arabia</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFEDB8C18E5FFFB2FD5FFD60DAFAFD57" author="COIFFAIT H" box="[742,903,667,689]" pageId="4" pageNumber="145" pagination="236 - 242" refId="ref7460" refString="COIFFAIT H. (1981): Insects of Saudi Arabia. Coleoptera: Fam. Staphylinidae, Subfam. Xantholininae, Staphylininae, Paederinae, Oxytelinae, Aleocharinae (Part 2). - Fauna of Saudi Arabia 3: 236 - 242." type="journal article" year="1981">COIFFAIT (1981</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFEDB8C18E5FFFB2FC28FD60DAB5FD57" author="COIFFAIT H" box="[913,968,667,689]" pageId="4" pageNumber="145" pagination="203 - 206" refId="ref7505" refString="COIFFAIT H. (1982): Staphylinides nouveaux d'Arabie Saoudite. - Bulletin de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de Toulouse 117: 203 - 206." type="journal article" year="1982">1982</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
